      "table_id": "table-003",
      "annotation_marker": "11",
      "annotation_type": "footnote",
      "annotation_text": "Footnote not printed in the source (Table 9 prints only footnotes 1-3). Table 9 is the Extended-Visit-Cycle variant of the Main Study, so this most likely corresponds to Table 7 (Main Study) footnote 24: \"PROs (FOSI, EQ-5D-5L, neuropathy questionnaire) will be collected while on study treatment every 8 weeks through the first year, then every 12 weeks thereafter. If the patient discontinues study treatment, assessment will occur at that time and then 8 weeks (± 2 weeks) later, regardless of status of subsequent treatment. PROs should be administered before conducting any other procedures.\"",
      "annotation_scope": "activity",
